    {
      "text": "A 20 year old female presents with severe acne and is prescribed isotretinoin 1 mg/kg. After two months of treatment, she reports dry skin, dry lips and dry eyes. Laboratory tests reveal mild elevation of liver enzymes. What is the most appropriate initial step in managing her side effects?",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "text": "Discontinue isotretinoin immediately and switch to an alternative oral acne medication.",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "text": "Advise the patient to use moisturizers, lip balm and artificial tears",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "text": "Decrease the dosage of isotretinoin and monitor liver enzymes regularly",
          "correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "D",
          "text": "Both B and C",
          "correct": true
        }
      ],
      "correct_answer": "D. Both B and C",
      "question_images": [],
      "explanation_images": [],
      "explanation": "<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:633px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Side Effects of Isotretinoin</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Side Effect</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p><strong>Treatment Solution</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Xerosis (dryness)</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Use moisturizers and hydrating agents <strong>(Option B)</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Cheilitis (dry lips)</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Use moisturizers and lip balms<strong> (Option B)</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Skin <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"0f4e78e9121692777203594ba840cc\">fragility</span> and dermatitis</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Avoid irritants and use gentle skin care products</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Rashes and erythema</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Topical corticosteroids if necessary</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Dry eyes</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Use artificial <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"1717bdb5d21692777200d45e31ceed\">tears</span> and lubricating eye drops<strong> (Option B)</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Depression</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Discontinue <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"e6a88ded8b1692777190caead269e4\">isotretinoin</span> and seek health professionals\u2019 advice as psychiatric side effects may occur in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"8b61bc6e361692777180695ac33e91\">acne</span> patients regardless of <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"e6a88ded8b1692777190caead269e4\">isotretinoin</span> use.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Liver test abnormalities</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Monitor liver function tests regularly, consider dose adjustment <strong>(Option C)</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Increased <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"5a7c641abc16927771852d9d7cd600\">creatine</span> phosphokinase (CPK) levels</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Monitor levels, adjust physical activity, and consider dose reduction</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Increased <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"00472d632e1692777189a71b99d4a9\">homocysteine</span> levels</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Monitor levels, dietary modifications, and consider supplementation</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #cccccc; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Stevens-Johnson syndrome</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #cccccc; border-left:1px solid #cccccc; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #cccccc; vertical-align:top\">\n<p>Discontinue <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"e6a88ded8b1692777190caead269e4\">isotretinoin</span> and seek immediate medical attention</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n\n\n<p style='font-size: 10px; color: #808080; font-style: italic;'></p>",
